This version of coin compare lets you track your cryptocurrency portfolio, your profit/loss, total coins you own across different Indian exchanges.

	1) Create an account ie., Register yourselves.
	2) Add transactions that you done in different exchanges using 'Add' button.
	3) Fill all the fields like price,exchange,type of coin,transaction date etc.
	4) This adds a new record into the database against this transaction.
	5) You can track your portfolio in your home page. 
	6) The profit/loss is shown as both in rupees as well as percentage.  